'''Tlokweng ''' ke toropo e e gaufi le toropokgolo ya [[Botswana|Botswana]], [[Botswana|Gaborone]], mo kgaolong ya [[Botswana|borwa-botlhaba]]. E ka tsewa e le bontlha bongwe jwa [[Gaborone|Gaborone]]. Tlokweng o ka kwa ntlheng e nngwe ya noka,gape o mo tseleng e e yang kwa molelwaneng wa [[Aferika Borwa|Aferika Borwa]], molelwane o dikhilomethara tse di lesome le botlhano kwa botlhaba. Mo palong batho ya 2001 batho ba ne ba le dikete tse masome a mabedi le bongwe, lekgolo le masome a mararo le boraro.<ref>{{cite web
